# Project: Promptura (Prompt Iteration UI)

Goal:
- Help users find the best prompt for a task by iterating:
  1) generate N candidate prompts
  2) run each prompt to produce outputs
  3) display prompt + outputs
  4) user selects best pairs and adds notes
  5) refine and generate next batch (repeat)

Modalities (must be extensible):
- text-to-text
- text-to-image
- (future) image-to-text, etc.

Non-goals (for MVP unless explicitly asked):
- complex auth/roles
- heavy multi-tenant enterprise concerns
- real-time collaboration
